Class MersenneTwister64

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.math.impl.cern.RandomEngine
      • com.opengamma.strata.math.impl.cern.MersenneTwister

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, DoubleUnaryOperator, IntUnaryOperator
    public class MersenneTwister64
extends MersenneTwister
    Same as MersenneTwister except that method raw() returns 64 bit random numbers instead of 32 bit random numbers.
    Version:
    1.0, 09/24/99
    See Also:
    MersenneTwister, Serialized Form
